Please see README.original for Python version 2.7.5 README file.
================================================================

wget http://www.python.org/ftp/python/2.7.5/Python-2.7.5.tar.bz2
tar -jxf Python-2.7.5.tar.bz2
cd Python-2.7.5/

After extraction Python source code,

first 

./configure # for host computer, no need to set CC, PATH variables.

make python Parser/pgen

then,

mv python python_for_build
mv Parser/pgen Parser/pgen_for_build

these executables are used while python compilation.

make distclean # to clean configure outputs like Makefile

Set system variables: CC, PATH.

Download this patch:
http://bugs.python.org/file31991/Python-2.7.5-xcompile.patch

Apply the patch:
patch -p3 < Python-2.7.5-xcompile.patch

./configure --host=arm-linux-gnueabihf --build=x86-linux --prefix=/python --disable-ipv6 ac_cv_file__dev_ptc=no ac_cv_file__dev_ptmx=no

Manually edit Makefile and set:

PYTHON_FOR_BUILD=./python_for_build

make

make install DESTDIR=~/python
